This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it presents a deep neural network for unsupervised learning. The paper also deals with image modeling, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of residual connections, which is a common technique in deep learning and could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of recurrent layers also suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with natural language processing, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language).
